{"tid":633610,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單的科學，對人生哲理的啟示","createTime":"2018-04-18T12:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T17:15:12.000Z","uid":149978,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d78c35dc462d579f9c230bdf5cf7305f6cd551e8","tid":633610,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"地球，眼看為平，實際為圓。<br />\n<br />\n人眼看，太陽繞地，實際上，地繞太陽。<br />\n<br />\n細菌病毒，眼看不到，殺傷力最大。<br />\n<br />\n老虎獅子，貌似強勁，實為瀕臨絕種，受保護動物。<br />\n<br />\n蚊蟲，表面小生物，實為人類最大殺手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這說明，世事難明，難理解<br />\n<br />\n我們人類看起來最真的，不一定真。<br />\n我們人類看起來最荒謬的，有可能才是事實的真相。"},{"pid":"dc66c877a30e8acc39b7b56e885a50d8cdaea67e","tid":633610,"uid":50744,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"港女嘅波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4efeafd961d787158a66181aeaa9ff5ca3bd029","tid":633610,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc66c877a30e8acc39b7b56e885a50d8cdaea67e","tid":633610,"uid":50744,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"港女嘅波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a110629f4db063acd3b01a39fc07b132bdc52ed2","tid":633610,"uid":59536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc66c877a30e8acc39b7b56e885a50d8cdaea67e","tid":633610,"uid":50744,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"港女嘅波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"變幻球"},{"pid":"20e2d67c9f08f13a4b775a7870657b0834dbb8f4","tid":633610,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:11:01.000Z","msg":"21世紀現代例子：<br />\n<br />\n比特幣，bitcoin，貌似投資騙局，虛擬無用，實為世紀升值最強投資產品，即使政府想取締佢都極為困難。"},{"pid":"56cc7be81